  _gtkmodule_la-gtkmodule.lo definition of __PyGObject_API in section (__DATA,__common)
  _gtkmodule_la-pygtktreemodel.lo definition of __PyGObject_API in section (__DATA,__common)
  _gtkmodule_la-pygtkcellrenderer.lo definition of __PyGObject_API in section (__DATA,__common)
  make[2]: *** [_gtkmodule.la] Error 1
<<
